Plushies are system that allows you to equip Plushies to gain extra stats. You can only have one of each plush.

Stats:
Health
Speed
Regeneration
Defense
Damage
Damage Types (Melee, Ranged, Affliction, Ammo-Based, etc.)
Affliction Chance
Luck (Dodge Chance)
Loot Bonus

DANGANRONPA:
Makoto - +2% Dodge Chance
Taka - +2% Defense
Togami - +1 Loot (1 extra gun per mission)
Mondo - +2% Blunt Damage
Leon - +10% Club Damage
Hifumi - +5% Confused Affliction Chance
Yasuhiro - +30% Cursed Affliction Chance
Chihiro - +25% Crypto Zombie Teleportation Cooldown
Sayaka - +5% Dagger Damage
Kyoko - -25% Invis Zombie Invisibility
Aoi + +4% Speed
Toko - +1% Regeneration
G. Jack - +5% Sharp Damage
Sakura - +10% Damage
Celestia - +10% Fire Affliction Chance
Junko - +20% Despair Affliction Chance
Mukuro - +5% Gun Damage
Monokuma - +30% Despair Affliction Chance

Hajime - +2% Health
